{"tid":1804398,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"北區招聘博覽周五上水免費舉行 提供4600空缺","createTime":"2019-12-31T03:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:19:30.000Z","uid":332903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"34aa070623ad83f134838ed3e038ca0ef2c87ec3","tid":1804398,"uid":332903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:14:38.000Z","msg":"博覽會共有72間機構參加，其中65間於會場設置櫃位，進行即場招聘。該等機構主要來自飲食、零售及物業管理業，合共提供超過4600個職位空缺。其餘7間則為培訓機構，為入場人士介紹培訓課程。博覽會於下午安排了兩項工藝及技能示範項目，包括沖廁水箱維修保養及電弧焊模擬操作。<br />\n<br />\n參與機構提供的職位類別相當廣泛，包括慈善推廣教育大使、診所助理、店務員、文員、保安員、司機、技術員、馬術事務助理、倉務員、收銀員、廚師、侍應、陪老員及美容顧問等。求職人士如欲進一步了解空缺詳情，<a href=\"http://可瀏覽勞工處互動就業服務網站www.jobs.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%AF%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%95%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.jobs.gov.hk&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=0e684897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">可瀏覽勞工處互動就業服務網站www.jobs.gov.hk</a>。<br />\n<br />\n博覽會中，約77%為全職空缺，大部分月薪介乎1萬元至1.9萬元。超過99%職位空缺的學歷要求為中六或以下，大約72%的職位空缺無需相關工作經驗。<br />\n<br />\n求職人士可即場遞交申請，有機會即場接受僱主面試，亦可在勞工處的櫃位查詢該處提供的就業計劃及服務。<br />\n<br />\n博覽會於上午11時至下午5時30分在上水百和路19號保榮路體育館（鄰近上水官立中學）舉行，入場費全免。<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191231/_2019123110535084937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191231%2F_2019123110535084937.jpg&h=5ccdf7d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ec052b97bf66ed0a31b90572a5a405d138d8dcf","tid":1804398,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:19:30.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=40657826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=1b932867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要24000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=6ee3bc4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要6000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=eda64407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">deadline fighters 請出招</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}